description:
Comedic power-couple Natasha Leggero (ANOTHER PERIOD) and Moshe Kasher (HONEYMOON STANDUP SPECIAL) are here for a brand new episode of Unqualified! First, Moshe describes his regrettable roof-climbing experience and the group discusses the stereotypes of stand-up comedians. After that, they talk about dating within the same profession and getting their starts in Hollywood. Then, Anna asks some dating deal breakers and Moshe recounts an interesting sexual encounter of his single days. Later, they call Carly, who is unsure if she should reveal her romantic feelings to a long-time friend, which leads them into an important conversation on the expectations of the male pursuit and expected gender roles in dating. Tune in & enjoy!
